{"tid":2185951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府信任度全民公投開催中 暫時有3.7%市民支持政府","createTime":"2020-09-02T15:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T15:11:14.000Z","uid":331739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb82f2da79ba09f5224f5d3763884ff5192c334","tid":2185951,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府表示，由今日（2日）早上8時至晚上8時，共有約15.2萬名市民經全民自願檢測計劃，在全港各社區檢測中心登記採樣；自計劃在昨日（1日）開展以來，累計合共有約27.8萬人在檢測中心登記檢測。</blockquote><br />\n宣傳咗成個月 請咗一堆偽人嚟幫手 <br />\n準備坐定定 感謝中央出手打救香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞咗兩日 終於搵到3.7%市民支持政府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 唔知14日後會有幾多人呢"},{"pid":"1892ebe61ec4f7413be52aa6c62e0a22ad4d15c2","tid":2185951,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"不是暫時，是到頂"},{"pid":"8d4924cf342958a17661a9b2a99ab9749c4c921b","tid":2185951,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"照目前比例<br />\n有廿幾%至30%人參加"}]}